                problemTitle: "Users drop off before seeing value",
                problemDescription: "Your conversion funnel is leaking. Users sign up but quickly abandon ship before experiencing your product's core benefits. This not only hurts your bottom line but also creates a negative feedback loop as frustrated users share their experiences.",
