                question: "What's your design toolkit?",
                answer: "We leverage cutting-edge tools including Figma for design, Miro for collaboration, and Hotjar for insights. Our AI-powered analytics tools help us make data-driven decisions. This modern stack ensures efficient workflows and measurable results."
            },
            {
                question: "How do you align design with business goals?",
                answer: "We start by deeply understanding your business objectives and KPIs. Our proven positioning framework helps identify your unique market advantage. Every design decision is measured against conversion metrics and growth targets, ensuring tangible business impact."
            },
            {
                question: "Can you improve our existing product?",
                answer: "Absolutely. We excel at product evolution. Our process starts with a comprehensive audit of your current product, user data analysis, and opportunity mapping. We then create a phased improvement plan that delivers results without disrupting your business operations."
            },
            {
                question: "How do you handle complex B2B SaaS products?",
                answer: "Complexity is our specialty. We've successfully simplified numerous complex B2B SaaS products through our systematic approach. Our fresh perspective often reveals simplification opportunities that internal teams miss, leading to more intuitive user experiences."
            },
            {
                question: "How do you manage project resources?",
                answer: "We maintain a lean team structure where each designer handles 2-3 projects maximum. This ensures dedicated attention to your project while maintaining flexibility for urgent needs. We never overcommit our resources, guaranteeing consistent quality and availability."
            },
            {
                question: "What's your satisfaction guarantee?",
                answer: "We offer a 100% satisfaction guarantee - if you're not completely satisfied, you don't pay. Our iterative approach includes regular checkpoints and feedback loops, ensuring we stay aligned with your vision and deliver exceptional results."
            },
            {
                question: "How do you work with development teams?",
                answer: "We provide comprehensive support to development teams through detailed specifications, interactive Figma prototypes, and component libraries. Our designers remain available throughout implementation to ensure smooth handoff and address any technical challenges."
            },
            {
                question: "What's your pricing structure?",
                answer: "We offer flexible pricing options including hourly rates (€110/hour, €95/hour for smaller companies) and project-based pricing. Each proposal includes a detailed project plan with clear deliverables and timeline. We customize pricing based on your specific needs and project scope."
            }
        ]}
    />

    <!-- Blog Preview Section -->
    <BlogPreviewSection 
        title="Our latest thoughts" 
        allPostsLink="/en/blog" 
        showAllPostsButtonText="Read all articles →"
        posts={latestPosts}
    />

</BaseLayout>

<style>
    .team-grid {
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column; /* Stack vertically by default (mobile) */
        align-items: center; /* Center items horizontally in column layout */
        gap: var(--spacing-lg);
    }

    .team-member {
        text-align: center; /* Ensure text inside member card is centered */
    }

    /* Apply row layout for medium screens and up */
    @media (min-width: 768px) {
        .team-grid {
            flex-direction: row; /* Arrange side-by-side */
            justify-content: center; /* Center items horizontally in row layout */
        }
    }
</style>
